@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_owgzem(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.abs(v0 + 0.04) / (v0 + 0.89 / v0 + 0.13)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(0.48) / (wp.exp(v2 + 0.35) + (v0 + 0.69 * tmp + 0.77)))
    tmp = v1
    v0 = (tmp + 0.35)
    v0 = v1
    v1 = wp.cos(0.10)
    v2 = ((v2 / wp.abs(tmp + 0.96)) + 0.42)
    data[tid] = v0
